{"tid":1793910,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"想講好耐，唔好再食元朗田中！","createTime":"2019-12-22T17:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T14:30:06.000Z","uid":153880,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"14a5bb56912646c77247d39372357841ddef5416","tid":1793910,"uid":153880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"話說半年前<br />\n下午12點佢開舖嘅時候我同男友就去咗做第一個食客<br />\n嗌左個魚生飯(好似係)<br />\n一食 個帶子臭撚到我即刻lur返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其他都食晒... GG...<br />\n<br />\n就嗰晚同第二日我痾左十幾二十次 <br />\n好啦痾清晒 但係<br />\n我男友就感冒 腸胃炎但屙唔晒食左止瀉藥<br />\n<br />\n過左一個星期<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢屎窟生左個雞蛋咁大嘅野</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生原來有細菌入左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到要入急症室開刀抽晒啲濃佢 痛撚到PK <br />\n<br />\n有打過去1823投訴 佢搵人check左話d魚生冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家仲有少少腫 但已經唔痛<br />\n<br />\n大家慎防呢間田中 以免中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc917e83af3bcb20d43b6e588c03f2539c8b3e1","tid":1793910,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"藍店?"},{"pid":"1e58e97dabcd959f184c6e3a3b7a0c9629d1dfcb","tid":1793910,"uid":17721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:37:32.000Z","msg":"自從搬左過果邊都無再食過 <br />\n都好多年下 好似差左好多"},{"pid":"883f914af63f891397360649dc009b1c4061e24e","tid":1793910,"uid":153880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fc917e83af3bcb20d43b6e588c03f2539c8b3e1","tid":1793910,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"藍店?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"唔知。。。"},{"pid":"27f1462326bdeb1ef2277632567b4779dd30da2a","tid":1793910,"uid":57365,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"4fc917e83af3bcb20d43b6e588c03f2539c8b3e1","tid":1793910,"ui